data.description: Next to Jessieville School! Newly updated 3-bed 2 bath on approx 1.38acres with attached carport & added detached 16x 28 garage perfect for your boat! or workshop! or home-office! Double hung insulated windows, heat pump that is only 2 years old, a roof less than 10 years old, gorgeous original hardwood floors in the living area, new carpet in the bedrooms, huge master suite with an added heated & cooled sunroom, a beautifully manicured yard & fertile garden spot, a large laundry room & more! AGENT REMARKS
